{
  "video_id": "_7t6Ry4PlTo",
  "title": "The business benefits of doing good | Wendy Woods",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12800.0,
      "end_time": 14456.0,
      "text": "A few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14480.0,
      "end_time": 17960.0,
      "text": "all the developed countries in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17120.0,
      "end_time": 18376.0,
      "text": "the wealthier ones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18400.0,
      "end_time": 20134.0,
      "text": "and all of the charities"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 23696.0,
      "text": "together donated about 200 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23720.0,
      "end_time": 25896.0,
      "text": "to developing countries in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25920.0,
      "end_time": 27896.0,
      "text": "the ones that bear most of the burden,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27920.0,
      "end_time": 30816.0,
      "text": "the heaviest burden of the world&#39;s biggest problems:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 30840.0,
      "end_time": 34880.0,
      "text": "poverty, hunger, climate change and inequality."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35640.0,
      "end_time": 37616.0,
      "text": "That same year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37640.0,
      "end_time": 44000.0,
      "text": "businesses invested in those same countries 3.7 trillion dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 45200.0,
      "end_time": 48336.0,
      "text": "Now, I get to travel a lot in my work"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48360.0,
      "end_time": 50896.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m privileged to see the amazing things"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50920.0,
      "end_time": 53496.0,
      "text": "that NGOs and some governments are doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53520.0,
      "end_time": 55640.0,
      "text": "with some of that 200 billion dollars:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56320.0,
      "end_time": 58416.0,
      "text": "helping malnourished children"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58440.0,
      "end_time": 61215.0,
      "text": "or families that don&#39;t have access to clean water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61240.0,
      "end_time": 63480.0,
      "text": "children who wouldn&#39;t be educated otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64879.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67950.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67120.0,
      "end_time": 71856.0,
      "text": "because the biggest problems in our world need trillions"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 71880.0,
      "end_time": 73320.0,
      "text": "not just billions."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74160.0,
      "end_time": 77816.0,
      "text": "So if we&#39;re going to make lasting and significant progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77840.0,
      "end_time": 80816.0,
      "text": "in the big challenges in our world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80840.0,
      "end_time": 82656.0,
      "text": "we need business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82680.0,
      "end_time": 85976.0,
      "text": "both the companies and the investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86000.0,
      "end_time": 87520.0,
      "text": "to drive the solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88760.0,
      "end_time": 92400.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s talk about what business should do."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93120.0,
      "end_time": 94456.0,
      "text": "And when I say that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94480.0,
      "end_time": 98576.0,
      "text": "you probably think that I&#39;m going to talk about corporate philanthropy"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98600.0,
      "end_time": 101216.0,
      "text": "or corporate social responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101240.0,
      "end_time": 104560.0,
      "text": "CSR is the norm today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104800.0,
      "end_time": 105480.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s very useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106000.0,
      "end_time": 109560.0,
      "text": "It provides a route for corporate generosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 113560.0,
      "text": "and that generosity is important to many corporations&#39; employees"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113800.0,
      "end_time": 114280.0,
      "text": "and customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115520.0,
      "end_time": 116776.0,
      "text": "But you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116800.0,
      "end_time": 118375.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just not big enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 119616.0,
      "text": "or strong enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119640.0,
      "end_time": 121176.0,
      "text": "or durable enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 121200.0,
      "end_time": 125536.0,
      "text": "to drive solutions to the biggest problems in our world today"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125560.0,
      "end_time": 127720.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s incremental cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129520.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131360.0,
      "text": "Even when business is booming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132240.0,
      "end_time": 136360.0,
      "text": "CSR just isn&#39;t designed to scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137360.0,
      "end_time": 139976.0,
      "text": "And then of course in a downturn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 140000.0,
      "end_time": 142479.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s one of the first programs to be cut."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143640.0,
      "end_time": 144976.0,
      "text": "So no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145000.0,
      "end_time": 146216.0,
      "text": "CSR --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146240.0,
      "end_time": 148256.0,
      "text": "corporate social responsibility --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 148280.0,
      "end_time": 150336.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 150360.0,
      "end_time": 152416.0,
      "text": "but TSI --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 152440.0,
      "end_time": 155790.0,
      "text": "total societal impact, is."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156360.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "TSI is the sum of all of the ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160400.0,
      "end_time": 162935.0,
      "text": "business can affect society"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162960.0,
      "end_time": 164800.0,
      "text": "by doing the real work:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165600.0,
      "end_time": 167856.0,
      "text": "thinking about their supply chains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167880.0,
      "end_time": 171696.0,
      "text": "working on their product design and manufacturing processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171720.0,
      "end_time": 173480.0,
      "text": "and their distribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 176160.0,
      "end_time": 178335.0,
      "text": "The real work of business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 178360.0,
      "end_time": 180416.0,
      "text": "when done with innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180440.0,
      "end_time": 185576.0,
      "text": "can actually create core business benefits for the company"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 190920.0,
      "text": "and it can solve the meaningful problems in our world today."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 192200.0,
      "end_time": 194000.0,
      "text": "So what does TSI look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 194560.0,
      "end_time": 196776.0,
      "text": "Focusing on TSI"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196800.0,
      "end_time": 201880.0,
      "text": "means incorporating social and environmental considerations."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202480.0,
      "end_time": 203696.0,
      "text": "And you know what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203720.0,
      "end_time": 206376.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that isn&#39;t completely new."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 206400.0,
      "end_time": 208280.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been thought about for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 209200.0,
      "end_time": 214950.0,
      "text": "But the hard part is that corporations almost exclusively still think"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 214120.0,
      "end_time": 216840.0,
      "text": "about something called TSR:"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 217440.0,
      "end_time": 219400.0,
      "text": "total shareholder returns."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220360.0,
      "end_time": 222176.0,
      "text": "But TSI --"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 222200.0,
      "end_time": 224536.0,
      "text": "total societal impact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 224560.0,
      "end_time": 228576.0,
      "text": "needs to stand alongside TSR"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 228600.0,
      "end_time": 233376.0,
      "text": "as an important and valid driver of corporate strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 233400.0,
      "end_time": 235120.0,
      "text": "and corporate decision-making."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 236400.0,
      "end_time": 239840.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve got the data to show you why and how."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 240480.0,
      "end_time": 244296.0,
      "text": "Some companies are already making this happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 244320.0,
      "end_time": 246495.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re beginning to make it happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 246520.0,
      "end_time": 249736.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you the story about Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249760.0,
      "end_time": 254280.0,
      "text": "Mars is the sixth-largest private company in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254960.0,
      "end_time": 256416.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256440.0,
      "end_time": 258656.0,
      "text": "they make some important products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258680.0,
      "end_time": 260240.0,
      "text": "like coffee and chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261120.0,
      "end_time": 262976.0,
      "text": "So not surprisingly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263000.0,
      "end_time": 265960.0,
      "text": "one of their most important ingredients is cocoa."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266680.0,
      "end_time": 270576.0,
      "text": "And some of their competitors are actually really worried"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 270600.0,
      "end_time": 274240.0,
      "text": "about the sustainability and the availability of cocoa supplies."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 275240.0,
      "end_time": 276456.0,
      "text": "But not Mars."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276480.0,
      "end_time": 280800.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re confident in the stable supply of that crop for the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 281440.0,
      "end_time": 282680.0,
      "text": "And why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 283320.0,
      "end_time": 287135.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because they partner with NGOs around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 287160.0,
      "end_time": 290400.0,
      "text": "that are working with small shareholder farmers."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 290800.0,
      "end_time": 293896.0,
      "text": "And those certification agency&#39;s NGOs"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 293920.0,
      "end_time": 297456.0,
      "text": "are working to help farmers improve crop yields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 297480.0,
      "end_time": 300800.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re making sure that they get a fair, premium, livable wage"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 301680.0,
      "end_time": 305496.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re helping them address any human rights potential issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305520.0,
      "end_time": 306856.0,
      "text": "in supply chains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306880.0,
      "end_time": 310960.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re helping minimize the effects on the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 310120.0,
      "end_time": 311440.0,
      "text": "like deforestation."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 312560.0,
      "end_time": 316256.0,
      "text": "Mars is on a path to 100 percent certified cocoa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 316280.0,
      "end_time": 320215.0,
      "text": "so this is a good program for farming communities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 320240.0,
      "end_time": 322816.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a good program for the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 322840.0,
      "end_time": 325416.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a good program for Mars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 325440.0,
      "end_time": 329400.0,
      "text": "who has solved a significant risk in their supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 330320.0,
      "end_time": 333960.0,
      "text": "But now let&#39;s get to the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333120.0,
      "end_time": 335520.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s actually really awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336280.0,
      "end_time": 340880.0,
      "text": "And let me explain exactly what the data points I&#39;m going to talk about are."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 341760.0,
      "end_time": 345896.0,
      "text": "When analysts and financial people look at companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345920.0,
      "end_time": 348536.0,
      "text": "they think about a lot of different statistics."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 348560.0,
      "end_time": 351976.0,
      "text": "I want to talk about two of the most important ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 352000.0,
      "end_time": 354896.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk about the overall value of a company --"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 354920.0,
      "end_time": 356696.0,
      "text": "its valuation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 356720.0,
      "end_time": 358600.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m going to talk about its margin."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 359160.0,
      "end_time": 362816.0,
      "text": "Basically the difference between all of its earnings"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 362840.0,
      "end_time": 364239.0,
      "text": "and all of its costs."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 365680.0,
      "end_time": 367776.0,
      "text": "So in our study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 367800.0,
      "end_time": 370960.0,
      "text": "we looked at oil and gas companies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 370120.0,
      "end_time": 371656.0,
      "text": "and the oil and gas companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 371680.0,
      "end_time": 375256.0,
      "text": "that are performing most strongly on TSI --"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 375280.0,
      "end_time": 376936.0,
      "text": "total societal impact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 376960.0,
      "end_time": 381239.0,
      "text": "see a 19 percent premium on their valuation."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 382120.0,
      "end_time": 383360.0,
      "text": "19 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 383960.0,
      "end_time": 385296.0,
      "text": "When they do really well"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 385320.0,
      "end_time": 388776.0,
      "text": "on things like minimizing the impact of their company"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 388800.0,
      "end_time": 391960.0,
      "text": "on the environment and water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 391120.0,
      "end_time": 395200.0,
      "text": "and when they have very strong occupational health and safety programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 395880.0,
      "end_time": 400536.0,
      "text": "And when they also add in strong employee training programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400560.0,
      "end_time": 405256.0,
      "text": "they get a 3.4 percentage point premium on their margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 405280.0,
      "end_time": 407200.0,
      "text": "But what about other industries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 407880.0,
      "end_time": 412960.0,
      "text": "Biopharmaceutical companies that are the strongest performers on TSI"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 412120.0,
      "end_time": 415160.0,
      "text": "see a 12 percent premium on their valuation."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 415600.0,
      "end_time": 419656.0,
      "text": "And then if they&#39;re best at expanded access to medicines --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 419680.0,
      "end_time": 422656.0,
      "text": "making medicines available for the people who need them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 422680.0,
      "end_time": 428320.0,
      "text": "they see a 6.7 percentage point premium on their gross margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 428960.0,
      "end_time": 432816.0,
      "text": "For the retail banks that are strongest on TSI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 432840.0,
      "end_time": 437895.0,
      "text": "they see a three percentage point premium on their valuation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 437920.0,
      "end_time": 441616.0,
      "text": "and then for those that differentially provide financial inclusion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 441640.0,
      "end_time": 444536.0,
      "text": "access to financial products for people who need it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 444560.0,
      "end_time": 450400.0,
      "text": "they see a 0.5 percentage point premium in their net income margin."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 450760.0,
      "end_time": 455216.0,
      "text": "Now, these numbers for banks may not seem very big,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 455240.0,
      "end_time": 457776.0,
      "text": "but in highly competitive industries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 457800.0,
      "end_time": 461360.0,
      "text": "even really small differences in margin matter a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 462560.0,
      "end_time": 465560.0,
      "text": "Now, what about those consumer goods companies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 465800.0,
      "end_time": 468359.0,
      "text": "the ones who make those products we love like coffee and chocolate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 469400.0,
      "end_time": 474136.0,
      "text": "Consumer goods companies that perform best on total societal impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 474160.0,
      "end_time": 478440.0,
      "text": "see an 11 percent valuation premium."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 479520.0,
      "end_time": 483960.0,
      "text": "And then if they do those smart things with their supply chain --"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 483120.0,
      "end_time": 486776.0,
      "text": "inclusive and responsibly sourcing their product --"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 486800.0,
      "end_time": 492800.0,
      "text": "they see a 4.8 percentage point premium on their gross margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 493240.0,
      "end_time": 494960.0,
      "text": "These numbers are significant."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 495720.0,
      "end_time": 499856.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve long known that things like fundamental financials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 499880.0,
      "end_time": 504800.0,
      "text": "growth rates and financial risks are key drivers of valuation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 505600.0,
      "end_time": 510856.0,
      "text": "but this rigorous analysis shows that social and environmental factors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 510880.0,
      "end_time": 513296.0,
      "text": "total societal impact measures --"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 513320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518000.00000000006,
      "text": "are also linked to valuations and margins."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 519440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520640.00000000006,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 521440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522736.00000000006,
      "text": "All else equal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 522760.0,
      "end_time": 525376.0,
      "text": "we didn&#39;t confuse the analysis with anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 525400.0,
      "end_time": 527336.0,
      "text": "All else being equal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 527360.0,
      "end_time": 533150.0,
      "text": "companies that perform strongly on social and environmental areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 533390.0,
      "end_time": 534559.0,
      "text": "achieve higher margins"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 535400.0,
      "end_time": 537240.0,
      "text": "and higher valuations."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 537960.0,
      "end_time": 540896.0,
      "text": "Now, I do understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 540920.0,
      "end_time": 545790.0,
      "text": "that companies are under a lot of short-term earnings pressures."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 546280.0,
      "end_time": 547896.0,
      "text": "But fortunately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 547920.0,
      "end_time": 551415.0,
      "text": "the investors who create some of this pressure"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 551440.0,
      "end_time": 556960.0,
      "text": "are actually more and more themselves starting to think longer-term"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 556120.0,
      "end_time": 559480.0,
      "text": "and starting to think with this TSI lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 560320.0,
      "end_time": 563776.0,
      "text": "In our conversations and surveys with investors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 563800.0,
      "end_time": 569415.0,
      "text": "75 percent of them say they expect to see improved revenues"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 569440.0,
      "end_time": 572216.0,
      "text": "and improved operating efficiency"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 572240.0,
      "end_time": 574920.0,
      "text": "for companies that are thinking with a TSI lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 576400.0,
      "end_time": 578376.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re actually starting to incorporate this"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 578400.0,
      "end_time": 580439.0,
      "text": "in their own investing behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 581480.0,
      "end_time": 583136.0,
      "text": "Last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 583160.0,
      "end_time": 587616.0,
      "text": "23 trillion in global assets"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 587640.0,
      "end_time": 591600.0,
      "text": "were in the category of socially responsible investing."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 592240.0,
      "end_time": 596800.0,
      "text": "Now, that&#39;s five billion over just the last two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 597560.0,
      "end_time": 602439.0,
      "text": "And it represents a quarter of the total global assets managed in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 605120.0,
      "end_time": 609480.0,
      "text": "I know that some of you may be cringing a little bit right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 610560.0,
      "end_time": 613415.0,
      "text": "Because in my decades of strategy consulting"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 613440.0,
      "end_time": 617520.0,
      "text": "with businesses and NGOs and governments around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 618400.0,
      "end_time": 621776.0,
      "text": "I find that many businesspeople"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 621800.0,
      "end_time": 625976.0,
      "text": "are hesitant to talk or even sometimes think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 626000.0,
      "end_time": 628920.0,
      "text": "the business benefits of doing good."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 630400.0,
      "end_time": 632736.0,
      "text": "They somehow think it&#39;s going to negate the value"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 632760.0,
      "end_time": 635456.0,
      "text": "of the benefits they&#39;re creating for society."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 635480.0,
      "end_time": 639560.0,
      "text": "Or that they&#39;ll be perceived as heartless or even mercenary."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 640760.0,
      "end_time": 643840.0,
      "text": "But we really do need to think differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 644920.0,
      "end_time": 646336.0,
      "text": "We need to think differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 646360.0,
      "end_time": 650496.0,
      "text": "because the only way we&#39;re going to make substantial progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 650520.0,
      "end_time": 653136.0,
      "text": "on the challenging problems of our time"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 653160.0,
      "end_time": 655280.0,
      "text": "is for business to drive the solutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 656440.0,
      "end_time": 660256.0,
      "text": "The job of business is to meet customer needs"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 660280.0,
      "end_time": 662295.0,
      "text": "and to do so profitably."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 662320.0,
      "end_time": 664000.0,
      "text": "They need to to survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 664880.0,
      "end_time": 670936.0,
      "text": "So one of the best ways for businesses to help ensure their own growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 670960.0,
      "end_time": 672936.0,
      "text": "their own longevity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 672960.0,
      "end_time": 677120.0,
      "text": "is to meet some of the hardest challenges in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 677720.0,
      "end_time": 679320.0,
      "text": "and to do so profitably."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 680400.0,
      "end_time": 683456.0,
      "text": "And when they do that innovatively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 683480.0,
      "end_time": 687760.0,
      "text": "when they do that ethically, responsibly, incredibly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 688600.0,
      "end_time": 690240.0,
      "text": "they should be proud."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 694200.0,
      "end_time": 697696.0,
      "text": "But if you still aren&#39;t sure about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 697720.0,
      "end_time": 699880.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s talk about a few more examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 700920.0,
      "end_time": 702856.0,
      "text": "What if you&#39;re a technology company"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 702880.0,
      "end_time": 705536.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re trying to grow your platform"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 705560.0,
      "end_time": 707719.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re trying to grow your customers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 708800.0,
      "end_time": 710560.0,
      "text": "Like, Airbnb."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 710800.0,
      "end_time": 715776.0,
      "text": "Airbnb has a portfolio of total societal impact activities."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 715800.0,
      "end_time": 718616.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re all spot-on their core business."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 718640.0,
      "end_time": 719976.0,
      "text": "In one initiative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 720000.0,
      "end_time": 722960.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re helping enable their community"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 722120.0,
      "end_time": 725576.0,
      "text": "to provide housing for free to those in disaster:"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 725600.0,
      "end_time": 727960.0,
      "text": "crisis survivors and relief workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 728680.0,
      "end_time": 731695.0,
      "text": "In another effort on their part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 731720.0,
      "end_time": 735536.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re actually helping and working with NGOs"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 735560.0,
      "end_time": 739880.0,
      "text": "to ensure that people can provide housing for free for refugees."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 741000.0,
      "end_time": 743336.0,
      "text": "Now, what I love about this program"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 743360.0,
      "end_time": 745976.0,
      "text": "is that I don&#39;t think most people would&#39;ve figured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 746000.0,
      "end_time": 747976.0,
      "text": "how to express their generosity"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 748000.0,
      "end_time": 751176.0,
      "text": "and open their homes for those in such dire need --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 751200.0,
      "end_time": 754216.0,
      "text": "certainly not so quickly or so easily or efficiently --"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 754240.0,
      "end_time": 756840.0,
      "text": "without this innovation by Airbnb."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 757840.0,
      "end_time": 759816.0,
      "text": "But at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 759840.0,
      "end_time": 762456.0,
      "text": "this is core to their corporate strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 762480.0,
      "end_time": 764496.0,
      "text": "and core to their growth"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 764520.0,
      "end_time": 769656.0,
      "text": "because they grow by increasing the number of hosts and guests"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 769680.0,
      "end_time": 771160.0,
      "text": "using their platform."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 772560.0,
      "end_time": 775536.0,
      "text": "But if they&#39;d only been thinking exclusively"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 775560.0,
      "end_time": 778550.0,
      "text": "about the return side of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 778800.0,
      "end_time": 781256.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure they would have ever figured out this route to growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 781280.0,
      "end_time": 783560.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re not charging transaction fees."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 784360.0,
      "end_time": 785816.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a pretty exciting way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 785840.0,
      "end_time": 788736.0,
      "text": "when they were thinking about how to bring their capabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 788760.0,
      "end_time": 790376.0,
      "text": "to a need in society"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 790400.0,
      "end_time": 793240.0,
      "text": "and at the same time drive their own growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 794760.0,
      "end_time": 797920.0,
      "text": "But what if you&#39;re trying to find new customer segments?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 798840.0,
      "end_time": 801960.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s move to South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 801120.0,
      "end_time": 803120.0,
      "text": "and let&#39;s talk about Standard Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 803680.0,
      "end_time": 805376.0,
      "text": "In South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 805400.0,
      "end_time": 806976.0,
      "text": "the government has a regulation"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 807000.0,
      "end_time": 812696.0,
      "text": "that requires all banks to donate 0.2 percent of their profits"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 812720.0,
      "end_time": 815720.0,
      "text": "to small and medium black-owned enterprises."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 816600.0,
      "end_time": 820376.0,
      "text": "And many banks just donate this to the entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 820400.0,
      "end_time": 822776.0,
      "text": "but Standard Bank thought creatively."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 822800.0,
      "end_time": 825455.0,
      "text": "And what they did is they took those funds"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 825480.0,
      "end_time": 829560.0,
      "text": "and they invested them in an independent trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 829800.0,
      "end_time": 834536.0,
      "text": "and they used that trust to fund loans to these black entrepreneurs."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 834560.0,
      "end_time": 837160.0,
      "text": "This is a highly leveraged model."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 837400.0,
      "end_time": 840616.0,
      "text": "They can support a lot more entrepreneurs with capital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 840640.0,
      "end_time": 843536.0,
      "text": "and because their success is completely intertwined"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 843560.0,
      "end_time": 846950.0,
      "text": "with the success of the entrepreneurs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 846120.0,
      "end_time": 850400.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re actually also using the fund to provide technical assistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 850800.0,
      "end_time": 853216.0,
      "text": "More entrepreneurs supported,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 853240.0,
      "end_time": 856800.0,
      "text": "more people and communities being lifted out of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 857520.0,
      "end_time": 859736.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s successful for Standard Bank."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 859760.0,
      "end_time": 863976.0,
      "text": "So successful that they&#39;re actually working on expanding this program"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 864000.0,
      "end_time": 866880.0,
      "text": "to other areas in their portfolio."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 867920.0,
      "end_time": 871616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not like we haven&#39;t been trying to solve the problems in our world"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 871640.0,
      "end_time": 872840.0,
      "text": "for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 873360.0,
      "end_time": 875560.0,
      "text": "We have, and they&#39;re still here."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 876600.0,
      "end_time": 878536.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re making progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 878560.0,
      "end_time": 880455.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not far enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 880480.0,
      "end_time": 881856.0,
      "text": "or fast enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 881880.0,
      "end_time": 883280.0,
      "text": "or universal enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 884120.0,
      "end_time": 885840.0,
      "text": "We need to flip our thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 887800.0,
      "end_time": 889216.0,
      "text": "We need to have business --"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 889240.0,
      "end_time": 892320.0,
      "text": "both companies and investors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 893200.0,
      "end_time": 898200.0,
      "text": "bring creative, innovative corporate strategy and capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 899200.0,
      "end_time": 902640.0,
      "text": "to solving the biggest problems in our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 903600.0,
      "end_time": 907400.0,
      "text": "And when they do that innovatively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 908240.0,
      "end_time": 909840.0,
      "text": "and when they do that"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
